  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p699856/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201409/d886771a769f4f12b9c41c26b8c87b7f.png\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; height: 305px; width: 460px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tDavid Cronenberg's Hollywood-centered family <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/melodrama\" target=\"_blank\">melodrama</a> Maps to the Stars marks the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/veteran\" target=\"_blank\">veteran</a> director's second straight film with Twilight alum Robert Pattinson after 2012's <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Cosmopolis\" target=\"_blank\">Cosmopolis</a>.大卫&middot;柯南伯格的这部以好莱坞为中心的家庭情节喜剧《星图》是这位经验丰富的导演与《暮光之城》演员罗伯特&middot;帕丁森在继2012年的《大都市》后合作的第二部电影。</p>\n<p>\n\tAlthough many still see Pattinson as vampire <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/heartthrob\" target=\"_blank\">heartthrob</a> Edward Cullen, Cronenberg told The Hollywood Reporter he could easily ignore Pattinson's Twilight past.虽然许多人仍然将帕丁森看作吸血鬼万人迷爱德华&middot;卡伦，但是柯南伯格告诉好莱坞记者，说他可以很轻松地忽略帕丁森过去在《暮光之城》中的刻板印象。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p699856/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p699856\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p594918/\">99%的人连Where are you from都不会回答！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p700335/\">为演蝙蝠侠 本&bull;阿弗莱克变身肌肉男</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"ht